To complete a brand new
installation of Anaconda,

31
00:01:21.05 --> 00:01:28.04
head over to www.cotinuum.io/downloads.

32
00:01:28.04 --> 00:01:31.06
Click on the Windows icon

33
00:01:31.06 --> 00:01:35.08
and select Python 3.6 version 64-bit.

34
00:01:35.08 --> 00:01:40.03
We don't want to install anything else.

35
